<paragraph id="IFRS17_B103" base="F55667531"><paranum>B103</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 17"/><data name="paranum" value="B103"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS17_P0866">To the extent that <xref base="F55666957" href="IFRS17_APPA.dita#IFRS17_APPA/IFRS17_P0532">insurance contracts<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0186"/></ph></xref> in a group affect the cash flows to <xref base="F55667014" href="IFRS17_APPA.dita#IFRS17_APPA/IFRS17_P0552">policyholders<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0291"/></ph></xref> of contracts in other groups (see <xref id="IFRS17_X0699" base="F59236491" href="IFRS17_gB67-B71.dita#IFRS17_gB67-B71/IFRS17_gB67-B71_TI">paragraphs B67&#x2013;B71</xref>), an entity shall assess whether the conditions in <xref id="IFRS17_X0700" base="F59236492" href="IFRS17_gB101-B118.dita#IFRS17_gB101-B118/IFRS17_gB101-B118_TI">paragraph B101</xref> are met by considering the cash flows that the entity expects to pay the policyholders determined applying <xref id="IFRS17_X0701" base="F59236493" href="IFRS17_B68.dita#IFRS17_B68">paragraphs B68&#x2013;B70</xref>.</p></body></paragraph>